Citation Requirement

If you use this project, in whole or in part, in your academic work (e.g., publications, theses, presentations, course materials, or derivative educational materials), you must cite the authors appropriately:

> Keshani K.  
> *Kunitz HMM Classification Project: HMM-based classification and evaluation pipeline for Kunitz domain proteins*.  
> University of Bologna, 2025.  
> GitHub: https://github.com/kianinsilico/labexam

If you are unsure how to cite this work, please contact the authors via GitHub Issues.

