Academic Integrity

This project was completed as a graded assignment at the University of Bologna. Reposting the repository, copying content (even partially), or claiming authorship of this work without permission and attribution constitutes academic dishonesty and a violation of both licensing and university policy.

Violations will be reported to GitHub and the University of Bologna as appropriate.

